<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>د ح ض<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٧٥٢ - د ح ض]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>دحَضَ يَدحَض، دَحْضًا ودُحوضًا، فهو داحِض، والمفعول مَدْحوض <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• دحَضتِ الحُجَّةُ:</span> بَطَلَت <span class="c1">" <span class="c3">{حُجَّتُهُمْ دَاحِضَةٌ}</span> "</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• دحَض الحُجَّةَ ونحوَها:</span> أَبْطَلَها ودَفَعَها بالحُجَّة والدَّليل.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>